Metadata.name: Blight of the Fumble Bee
Metadata.desc: Watch the bleary-eyed office drones run in panic as a pack of supercar-wielding wannabe 'gangstaz' relentlessly hurl themselves full speed into the side of an insurance office like demented lemmings first thing in the morning. Get a grip or take flight like a bee in this lapped stunt race around the spires of Los Santos City Centre. Big 'air, tubes, loops and ramps that will really test how much rubber is left on your tyres... GTA Mode available but not essential.

Metadata.name: Felopian Tubes
Metadata.desc: If you've ever wondered what it would be like to race through the skies of Los Santos in a stunt race that features not only a giant replica of the female reproductive system, but also a spin-drier simulator followed by an inverted ejaculation 8,000 feet above the city, this race is for you. If not, this race is still for you.

Metadata.name: Fear and Loathing in LS
Metadata.desc: Fear and Loathing in Los Santos. A cosmic journey around, over and through Mount Chiliad. Take a leap of faith, open the doors of your perception, enter the void and then trip over the light fantastic like a shaman after a good night out. You never know, this could well be more mind-blowing than the trepanning your brain will need after that final ten laps...
